The [[United States Census Bureau|U.S. Census Bureau]] identifies Calvary as a census-designated place, roughly equivalent to an incorporated place, for the purposes of statistics.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.census.gov/geo/reference/gtc/gtc_place.html|title=2010 Geographic Terms and Concepts - Place|last=Geography|first=US Census Bureau|website=www.census.gov|language=EN-US|access-date=2019-03-11}}</ref>  Calvary was first listed as a CDP in the [[2010 U.S. census]].<ref name=2010CensusP2/><ref name=2000CensusGA/>

